// https://www.shadertoy.com/view/DdccDr hexagonally grouped weaved lines, written 2023 by jt
// hexagonal variant of https://www.shadertoy.com/view/DdccR8 three directions city grid parts
// modification of https://www.shadertoy.com/view/msdcRr three directions city grid hash
// variant of https://www.shadertoy.com/view/DljBDm three directions city grid patch
// https://www.shadertoy.com/view/dtBBRw three dir grid patches essence
// 2d essence of https://www.shadertoy.com/view/DtsBWl three directional grid patches

// Like in the original shader two lines (at distance one-third) parallel to one side of randomly oriented triangle.
// In addition triangles are grouped: every six adjacent triangles forme a hexagon, share orientation.
// Click to show underlying triangular grid.

// tags: procedural, 2d, triangle, triangles, patterns, random, barycentric, pattern, hexagonal, braided, hexagonally, grouped, weaved

